Aim: To build a rich text editor for writing articles. A preview button to the html preview. A sbumit button which is generate the string with HTML tags and style decoration to store into DB so that when it gets fetch, the styles and view remains same.

This rich text editor can be used anywhere like
<div class="articleforge"></div>
<script src="ourjsscript.js"></script>

Project name is ArticleForge so keep that naming in mind. People should use articleforge to use this.

My plan is to put into github public repo so that people can freely use. It would be better if people can use it as dependency in laravel.

Features:
- Full screen typing in editor
- Align text (left right center justify)
- bold
- font size
- font color
- select h1 to h6 tag
- underline
- italic
- add image
- image alignment left right center

My Approch:
- Generate the UI file in html
- JS file for processing which includes sanitization and validation of content
- Validation include no js or script tag i.e. no hacking attacks
- This js file will generate the output string with HTML tags and style decoration to store into DB


